Summary: ORANGEISH WHITE OBR MOVED SLOWLY FROM SOUTH TO NW MAKING NO NOISE
Object Flight Path: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
divs: Sighting Details I AM CURRENTLY IN A CRISIS WITH THE REPEATED SIGHTINGS OF LIGHTS IN THE SKY OF COLOMBIA TN. IN THE MONTH OF APRIL I'VE HAD A DOZEN SIGHTINGS. THE OBJECTS RANGE FROM ORANGE-ISH WHITE WITH A SMALL RED LIGHTS, ON WHAT APPEARS TO BE THE BACK OF THE OBJECT, TO BLINKING RED AND WHITE LIGHTS WITH A BLUE LIGHT EVERY NOW AND THEN. THESE PARTICULAR BLINKING LIGHTS WERE ACCOMPANIED BY YET OTHER OBJECTS THAT HAD THE SAME LIGHT PATTERNS. I COUNTED FOUR INDIVIDUAL OBJECTS WITH THIS SAME LIGHT CONFIGURATION. I AM A LITTLE STREESED OUT AND WANT TO KNOW WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON HERE. THE SIGHTINGS BEGAN AT THE BEGINNING OF THE MONTH AND HAVE NOT STOPPED. I WISH SOMEONE COULD REACH OUT AND TELL ME WHAT TO DO WITH THIS. I HAVE TAKEN MANY PICS AND VIDEO WITH MY CELL PHONE AND A CAMERA, WHICH I PLAN ON GETTING DEVELOPED. THE CELL PHONE IS FULL OF ORBS AND UNEXPLAINED LIGHTS. PLEASE HELP,JON
